&lt;p&gt;Nobu Hotel Toronto is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees. If contacted for an employment opportunity, please advise Human Resources if you require accommodation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nobutorontojobs.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(160, 146, 112);&quot;&gt;VEW ALL JOBS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are currently seeking a skilled and dedicated individual to join our pastry team as a Full-Time Pastry Chef de Partie at Nobu Hotel Toronto. As Pastry Chef de Partie, you will play a crucial role in ensuring the smooth operation of the pastry kitchen, including preparation, production, and execution of Nobu&#39;s signature pastry offerings. If you are passionate about pastry arts, have a strong foundation in pastry techniques, and thrive in a fast-paced kitchen environment, we invite you to join us at Nobu and showcase your talent as a Pastry Chef de Partie.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform food preparation tasks and production of various pastry items including cakes, tarts, desserts, and breads, ensuring high standards of quality, taste, and presentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute advanced pastry techniques such as mixing, shaping, baking, and decorating with precision and attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with other members of the pastry team to ensure efficient workflow, priority of orders, and timely delivery of pastry items during busy service periods.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute creative ideas to menu development, suggesting improvements and innovations to enhance the dining experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain strict adherence to food safety and hygiene standards, ensuring compliance with all relevant regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide guidance and support to junior members of the pastry kitchen, helping them develop their skills and knowledge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in monitoring inventory levels and placing orders for supplies as needed, minimizing waste and ensuring freshness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate flexibility and adaptability in a fast-paced environment, remaining calm under pressure and adjusting to changing priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure cleanliness and organization in the pastry kitchen area, including equipment and workstations, to uphold sanitation standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with front-of-house colleagues to fulfill special requests and dietary requirements, striving to exceed guest expectations at all times.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience as a Pastry Chef de Partie or a similar role in a fine dining kitchen environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive knowledge of culinary techniques, ingredients, and kitchen equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational and time-management skills, with the ability to multitask effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to work collaboratively as part of a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail and a passion for creating exceptional culinary experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Certification from a culinary school or equivalent training program is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Food Handler certification.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work flexible shifts including evenings, weekends, and holidays as required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to stand for extended periods and lift heavy objects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join our team and be part of an exciting culinary journey! If you meet the above requirements and are eager to contribute your talents to our kitchen, please submit your application including your resume detailing your relevant experience. We look forward to hearing from you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nobu Hotel Toronto is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees. If contacted for an employment opportunity, please advise Human Resources if you require accommodation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nobutorontojobs.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(160, 146, 112);&quot;&gt;VEW ALL JOBS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are currently seeking a skilled and dedicated individual to join our culinary team as a Full-Time Sushi Prep Cook at Nobu Restaurant, Toronto. In this role, you will be responsible for assisting the sushi chefs in the preparation and assembly of ingredients for sushi and sashimi dishes, ensuring the highest standards of quality, freshness, and presentation. If you have a passion for Japanese cuisine, attention to detail, and thrive in a fast-paced kitchen environment, we invite you to join us at Nobu and showcase your talent as a Sushi Prep Cook.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare sushi ingredients according to established recipes and standards, including slicing fish, chopping vegetables, and cooking rice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all ingredients are fresh, properly portioned, and stored at the correct temperature.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in maintaining inventory levels by restocking ingredients and supplies as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep workstations clean and organized, following food safety and sanitation guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the sushi chef during service by assembling sushi rolls, sashimi plates, and other menu items.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with the setup and breakdown of the sushi station before and after service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively with other kitchen staff to coordinate food preparation and ensure timely service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow proper knife handling techniques and maintain sharp knives for safe and efficient food prep.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adhere to all company policies, procedures, and standards of food quality and presentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in training sessions and workshops to enhance sushi preparation skills and knowledg.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience working in a sushi restaurant or Japanese kitchen preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of sushi preparation techniques and familiarity with Japanese ingredients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and commitment to maintaining high standards of food quality and presentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and teamwork skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic understanding of food safety and sanitation principles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Physical ability to stand for extended periods and lift heavy objects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for sushi and Japanese cuisine is highly desirable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Legal right to work in Canada&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join our team and be part of an exciting culinary journey! If you meet the above requirements and are eager to contribute your talents to our kitchen, please submit your application including your resume detailing your relevant experience. We look forward to hearing from you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nobu Hotel Toronto is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees. If contacted for an employment opportunity, please advise Human Resources if you require accommodation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nobutorontojobs.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(160, 146, 112);&quot;&gt;VEW ALL JOBS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Quantum Coffee is a meeting place, a community centre and a destination for quality coffee. Quantum Coffee employees work to anticipate and fulfill customer needs, ensuring a welcoming environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Barista, you will work at various stations throughout the coffee bar, and will work with all others in the coffee bar during your scheduled shifts.&amp;nbsp; Baristas report to the Manager and Shift Supervisors as required.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Barista responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft specialty coffee beverages and serve baked goods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use Point-Of-Sale (POS) system and handle cash accurately&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact with customers, maintain customer service standard&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain safe and healthy work environments by following company standard operating procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restock supplies, detail oriented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills and ability to multitask in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cleaning of coffee machines and equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A positive attitude, a smile and a passion for coffee&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High volume experience, being able to work on multiple orders at once&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outgoing personality with strong work ethic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills &amp;amp; Abilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work as part of a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to read situations and problem solve quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to keep a calm demeanor during service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess a well-balanced repertoire of interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess strong verbal communication&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability to work flexible shifts, including weekends and holidays.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to stand/walk for the duration of a regular work shift, 6 - 8 hours&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intermittent bending, kneeling and squatting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasional carrying and lifting, up to 50lb&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary of Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of barista experience preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with TouchBistro point of sale is an asset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;While we sincerely appreciate all applications, only those candidates selected for an interview will be contacted.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Quantum Coffee is committed to maintaining a diverse work environment and is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. All qualified applicants, regardless of race, color, religion, gender, gender identity or expression, sexual orientation, national origin, genetics, disability, age, or veteran status will receive consideration for employment. If you have any accessibility requirements or concerns regarding the hiring process or employment with us, please notify us so we can provide suitable accommodation.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Quantum Coffee is a meeting place, a community centre and a destination for quality coffee. Quantum Coffee employees work to anticipate and fulfill customer needs, ensuring a welcoming environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Key Holder, you will work at various stations throughout the coffee bar, and will work with all others in the coffee bar during your scheduled shifts. The Key Holder reports to the Manager.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Holder Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use Point-Of-Sale (POS) system, cash handling and producing end of day sales reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Train, support and lead the team on the floor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide coaching to team members as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Go above and beyond to provide memorable experiences for our guests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Executes store operations during scheduled shifts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organizes opening and closing duties as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow Quantum Coffee operational policies and procedures, including those for cash handling and safety and security, to ensure the safety of all employees during each shift.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow up with baristas during the shift to ensure the delivery of customer service for all customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow health, safety and sanitation guidelines for all products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft specialty coffee beverages and serve baked goods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate any issues or concerns in a timely manner with the Manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A positive attitude, a smile, a passion for coffee and the ability to multitask&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills &amp;amp; Abilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to direct the work of others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to learn quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective oral communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work as part of a team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to read situations and problem solve quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to keep a calm demeanor during service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Availability to work flexible shifts, including weekends and holidays.&lt;/li&gt;
